commit.message: Updated tested-with clause to include GHC 9.6.3 and 9.8.1
Remove usage of Data.List.tail, which raises a warning in GHC 9.8+
Add minimum version to text-icu so benchmarks can be built with text>=2
CI: fix installation of ghc, cabal.
CI: Use ghc 9.6 for macos build and benchmark.
Run benchmark with 3 different ghc versions.
CI: use latest point release for each ghc version.
ALlow base 4.18 and add CI for ghc 9.6.

Disable doctests for ghc 9.4.2 CI build.

doctests doesn't build yet on ghc 9.4.2.
Update tested-with and CI to use ghc 9.4.2.

Allow base 4.17.  Closes #12.

Tested with ghc 9.4.

Bump to 0.3.1.1, update changelog.

Note that the test suite fails with ghc 9.2 (#8).
